  "subject": "POC ran-topology-adapter simulator",
  "commit_message": "POC ran-topology-adapter simulator\n\nThis simulates additional load during registration by listening for\nCM-handle LCM events, and when a CM-handle becomes READY, it sends\nREST requests to fetch inventory and model information from NCMP.\n\nIssue-ID: CPS-2526\nSigned-off-by: danielhanrahan <daniel.hanrahan@est.tech>\nChange-Id: Ie11472dc780dba992fe5c62b9c83d895a58d6eab\n",
